=Dragon King's Decree=

24
00:01:56,287 --> 00:01:59,445
=Episode 3=

25
00:02:01,150 --> 00:02:02,988
If you harm the innocent,

26
00:02:02,989 --> 00:02:04,949
your life is yours to lose.

27
00:02:05,469 --> 00:02:06,630
Just die already!

28
00:02:06,670 --> 00:02:08,709
If you've dirtied yourself,

29
00:02:08,710 --> 00:02:10,509
then wash away your sins.

30
00:02:12,150 --> 00:02:13,869
Why cling to lies

31
00:02:13,870 --> 00:02:15,870
and fall deeper into misery?

32
00:02:16,789 --> 00:02:18,908
Let nature be free.

33
00:02:18,909 --> 00:02:21,910
Let all things live as they please.

34
00:02:24,749 --> 00:02:26,910
Sink Feng Zhilou into the pond now!

35
00:02:29,430 --> 00:02:31,668
If I survive this,

36
00:02:31,669 --> 00:02:33,149
I swear I'll rise on my own

37
00:02:33,150 --> 00:02:34,989
and fight alongside the Dragons.

38
00:02:35,469 --> 00:02:37,389
I'll crush all of you under my feet!

39
00:02:37,390 --> 00:02:38,509
Fine.

40
00:02:38,870 --> 00:02:41,030
If that day ever comes,

41
00:02:41,150 --> 00:02:43,910
