without a spiritual root)

55
00:03:31,550 --> 00:03:32,910
(and can't cultivate martial arts,)

56
00:03:33,469 --> 00:03:35,549
(does that mean anyone can bully me)

57
00:03:35,789 --> 00:03:37,468
