154
00:08:55,709 --> 00:08:57,469
Are you fully awake right now?

155
00:08:57,470 --> 00:08:59,068
The Dragon himself is here
at Feng Manor.

156
00:08:59,069 --> 00:09:00,588
How dare you slander him?

157
00:09:00,589 --> 00:09:01,749
Feng Zhilou,

158
00:09:01,750 --> 00:09:02,869
how dare you hit me!

159
00:09:02,870 --> 00:09:04,149
Why wouldn't I?

160
00:09:04,150 --> 00:09:05,188
I meant to hit you.

161
00:09:05,189 --> 00:09:06,708
Do I need to pick a date for it?

162
00:09:06,709 --> 00:09:08,428
You owe me all of this.

163
00:09:08,429 --> 00:09:10,548
You had an affair with Lenghou Zong,

164
00:09:10,549 --> 00:09:12,029
plotted to frame and kill me,

165
00:09:12,390 --> 00:09:15,710
and used every filthy trick you could
to make Jia Yu destroy my name.

166
00:09:16,350 --> 00:09:17,908
You slandered the Dragons.

167
00:09:17,909 --> 00:09:18,588
Your mind

168
00:09:18,589 --> 00:09:20,430
is nothing but lust and corruption.

169
00:09:21,030 --> 00:09:22,788
As the family's legitimate daughter,

170
00:09:22,789 --> 00:09:23,869
you've acted arrogantly,

171
00:09:23,870 --> 00:09:25,188
seething with jealousy,

172
00:09:25,189 --> 00:09:26,269
constantly scheming,

173
00:09:26,270 --> 00:09:27,470
and intolerant of others!

174
00:09:29,030 --> 00:09:29,749
You!

175
00:09:29,750 --> 00:09:30,588
Miss Feng,

176
00:09:30,589 --> 00:09:31,948
don't provoke the Dragon God.

177
00:09:31,949 --> 00:09:33,229
Now get down on your knees

178
00:09:33,230 --> 00:09:34,190
and apologize!

179
00:09:34,270 --> 00:09:37,310
Do it!

180
00:09:38,709 --> 00:09:41,068
Do it!

181
00:09:41,069 --> 00:09:42,149
Do it now!

182
00:09:42,270 --> 00:09:43,710
Don't let her fool you!

183
00:09:44,829 --> 00:09:46,350
Dragon?

184
00:09:48,309 --> 00:09:49,269
Feng Zhilou,

185
00:09:49,270 --> 00:09:51,229
do you think you deserve the Dragon God?

186
00:09:51,230 --> 00:09:51,908
Demons!

187
00:09:51,909 --> 00:09:52,989
They're demons!

188
00:09:52,990 --> 00:09:54,668
Demons!

189
00:09:54,669 --> 00:09:55,188
Feng Yunqiao,

190
00:09:55,189 --> 00:09:56,590
shut your mouth!

191
00:09:58,110 --> 00:10:00,509
You made a mess in front of the Dragons

192
00:10:00,510 --> 00:10:01,788
and still refuse to own up to it?

193
00:10:01,789 --> 00:10:02,909
You!

194
00:10:03,069 --> 00:10:04,509
Are you trying to drag us down

195
00:10:04,510 --> 00:10:06,269
with you?

196
00:10:10,470 --> 00:10:12,749
What a shameful sight.

197
00:10:12,829 --> 00:10:14,989
You old, disrespectful fool,

198
00:10:14,990 --> 00:10:15,788
your conscience

199
00:10:15,789 --> 00:10:18,070
is no cleaner than hers.

200
00:10:18,110 --> 00:10:19,869
Who are you to judge her?

201
00:10:19,870 --> 00:10:20,989
Feng Zhilou,

202
00:10:20,990 --> 00:10:22,428
don't get carried away.

203
00:10:22,429 --> 00:10:22,989
That's right.

204
00:10:22,990 --> 00:10:24,470
What are you talking about?

205
00:10:24,669 --> 00:10:26,869
I'm talking about you, old man!

206
00:10:26,870 --> 00:10:29,788
You're full of talk about family honor
and meddling in everyone's affairs,

207
00:10:29,789 --> 00:10:31,828
but all you do is use your power
to boss people around.

208
00:10:31,829 --> 00:10:32,588
What's it?

209
00:10:32,589 --> 00:10:33,668
Just because you're old,

210
00:10:33,669 --> 00:10:35,188
no one can challenge you?

211
00:10:35,189 --> 00:10:35,869
You!

212
00:10:35,870 --> 00:10:36,668
Honestly,

213
00:10:36,669 --> 00:10:38,828
you're the biggest
troublemaker in this family!

214
00:10:38,829 --> 00:10:39,950
You!

215
00:10:43,429 --> 00:10:44,470
And you too.

216
00:10:44,549 --> 00:10:46,989
You abandoned your aging father at home

217
00:10:46,990 --> 00:10:48,908
and treated your wife like nothing.

218
00:10:48,909 --> 00:10:49,828
If your mother knew

219
00:10:49,829 --> 00:10:51,349
how you turned out,

220
00:10:51,350 --> 00:10:53,428
she'd be rolling in her grave!

221
00:10:53,429 --> 00:10:54,269
You!

222
00:10:54,669 --> 00:10:56,308
Your son is a treasure to you,

223
00:10:56,309 --> 00:10:57,908
and your daughter is disposable.

224
00:10:57,909 --> 00:10:59,548
You worked her to the bone

225
00:10:59,549 --> 00:11:01,629
and forced her
to marry an old man as a concubine.

226
00:11:01,709 --> 00:11:04,029
She ended up
throwing herself into the river.

227
00:11:04,150 --> 00:11:05,068
If I were her,

228
00:11:05,069 --> 00:11:06,229
I'd come back as a ghost

229
00:11:06,230 --> 00:11:07,790
and drag you down with me!

230
00:11:21,150 --> 00:11:22,269
Feng Qingfeng,

231
00:11:22,429 --> 00:11:23,909
surprising, isn't it?

232
00:11:24,030 --> 00:11:25,908
The person you were so eager
to see executed

233
00:11:25,909 --> 00:11:28,229
is standing here alive.

234
00:11:28,829 --> 00:11:30,310
Are you disappointed?

235
00:11:34,870 --> 00:11:36,229
Feng Manor

236
00:11:36,589 --> 00:11:38,269
may have given me life,

237
00:11:38,750 --> 00:11:40,029
but it never raised me.

238
00:11:41,230 --> 00:11:42,308
I may be a girl

239
00:11:42,309 --> 00:11:43,509
without a spiritual root,

240
00:11:44,110 --> 00:11:45,710
but I never deserved death.

241
00:11:46,949 --> 00:11:48,909
You framed me
and pinned false charges on me.

242
00:11:49,350 --> 00:11:51,190
You even tried to drown me.

243
00:11:51,870 --> 00:11:53,670
I've already repaid the life

244
00:11:54,270 --> 00:11:55,710
you gave me.

245
00:11:55,990 --> 00:11:57,190
From today on,

246
00:11:57,429 --> 00:11:59,149
we have nothing to do with each other.

247
00:12:00,270 --> 00:12:01,109
Zhilou,

248
00:12:01,110 --> 00:12:02,389
you've misunderstood.

249
00:12:07,150 --> 00:12:08,269
Zhilou,

250
00:12:08,350 --> 00:12:10,670
you're a daughter of the Feng family.

251
00:12:10,909 --> 00:12:12,948
You should follow our traditions

252
00:12:12,949 --> 00:12:14,790
and do your duty.

253
00:12:15,429 --> 00:12:17,629
If you want to leave,

254
00:12:17,709 --> 00:12:19,590
the only way is through marriage.

255
00:12:19,709 --> 00:12:20,989
Otherwise,

256
00:12:21,230 --> 00:12:23,350
you can never step out of this place.

257
00:12:23,949 --> 00:12:24,909
I'm...

258
00:12:25,150 --> 00:12:26,989
the Feng family head.

259
00:12:28,069 --> 00:12:29,869
I will stop you

260
00:12:29,990 --> 00:12:31,470
with my life.

261
00:12:33,390 --> 00:12:36,190
What a grand, mighty family head.

262
00:12:37,309 --> 00:12:38,749
